OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,6,Fwill follow for all, albeit hazy for
OL,7,Fmany, especially in the west. It will
OL,8,Fremain gusty across the high ground of
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall and around coastal
OL,10,Fareas. Feeling very warm in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear night as high cloud
OL,13,Fmoves away. Patchy cloud developing
OL,14,Falong the south coast of Devon but
OL,15,Fwinds turning lighter. Staying gusty
OL,16,Falong coastal areas and higher hills.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FWinds stay gusty in places,
OL,19,Fbut a fine and dry day for all. High
OL,20,Fcloud returns, turning the sun hazy in
OL,21,Fplaces, but feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
