OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny into the weekend with
OL,7,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,8,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,9,Ftemperatures to dip slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
